gapminder %>%

  filter(iso2 == "US" |
           name == "China" |
           name == "India" |
           name == "Japan") %>% 
  ggplot(aes(time, co2, col=factor(name))) +
  geom_line() +
  geom_point() +
  labs(x = "Time", y = "CO2", 
       col = "Country")

gapminder %>% 
  group_by(region, time) %>% 
  filter(!is.na(lifeExpectancy),
         !is.na(region)) %>% 
  summarize(avg = mean(lifeExpectancy)) %>% 
  arrange(start = 1960, end = 2019,
          rank(avg)) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% 
  mutate(growth = avg - lag(avg)) %>%
